name: pyviz_comms
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.2.0" %}

package:
  name: pyviz_comms
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/pyviz_comms/pyviz_comms-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b8c9dcbde01f3847843fb4d04c3b3f4de784920c71e44ced9dfbb560f6c92218

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=2.7
    - param
    - pip
    - jupyter-packaging
    - jupyterlab
    - notebook
  run:
    - python >=2.7
    - param

test:
  imports:
    - pyviz_comms

about:
  home: https://www.holoviz.org
  summary: Bidirectional communication for PyViz
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.txt

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jlstevens
    - philippjfr
